1211:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c **** /**
1212:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****   @brief         Processing function for the floating-point complex FFT.
1213:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****   @param[in]     S              points to an instance of the floating-point CFFT structure
1214:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****   @param[in,out] p1             points to the complex data buffer. Processing occurs in-place
1215:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****   @param[in]     ifftFlag       flag that selects transform direction
1216:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                    - value = 0: forward transform
1217:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                    - value = 1: inverse transform
1218:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****   @param[in]     bitReverseFlag flag that enables / disables bit reversal of output
1219:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                    - value = 0: disables bit reversal of output
1220:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                    - value = 1: enables bit reversal of output
1221:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****   @par Neon version
1222:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                      The neon version has a different API.
1223:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                      The input and output buffers must be
1224:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                      different.
1225:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                      There is an optional temporary buffer.
1226:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                      If the temporary buffer is not used, the
1227:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                      input buffer is modified.
1228:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                      The bit reverse flag is not more 
1229:Drivers/CMSIS_DSP/Source/TransformFunctions/arm_cfft_f32.c ****                      available in Neon version.
